Package com.github.kaktushose.jda.commands.annotations

All annotations that are needed to use this framework.

See: Description

  • Annotation Types Summary 
    Annotation Type Description
    Command
    Methods annotated with Command will be registered as a command at startup.
    CommandController
    Classes annotated with CommandController will be scanned at startup.
    Concat
    Parameters annotated with Concat will be assigned with a concatenated String of all remaining arguments.
    Inject
    Fields annotated with Inject will be assigned a value that is provided by a Producer declared within a Provider.
    Optional
    Parameters annotated with Optional are as the name says optional.
    Permission
    CommandController classes or Command methods annotated with Permission will require the user to have the given permissions in order to execute the command.
    Produces
    Methods annotated with Produces will be used to get the instance of a dependency.
